# Phase 1: Simple Fallback UI with Featured Projects

**Priority:** High | **Status:** 📋 Planned | **Complexity:** Low

## Context Links

- [Plan Overview](./plan.md)
- [v1 Analysis](./research/researcher-260211-1038-v1-zero-results-fallback.md)
- [v2 Current State](./reports/scout-260211-1038-v2-listing-current-state.md)

## Overview

Quick win implementation using already-loaded data. When search returns zero results, display featured projects and helpful messaging instead of blank page. No backend changes needed.

## Key Insights

**Data Already Available:**
- `featuredProjects` (5 items) - loaded in `[...slug].astro` line 236
- `seoMetadata` - title, description, content blocks
- `sideBlocks` - related regions, category info
- `provinceList` with counts - alternative locations

**No Additional API Calls Needed!**

## Requirements

### Functional Requirements

1. **Detect zero results** in `[...slug].astro` after `searchProperties()` returns
2. **Pass fallback flag** to `listing-grid.astro`
3. **Render fallback UI** with:
   - Clear messaging: "Không tìm thấy kết quả phù hợp với tiêu chí tìm kiếm"
   - Suggestion heading: "Gợi ý cho bạn" (Suggestions for you)
   - Featured projects grid (reuse existing data)
   - Optional: Links to nearby provinces/districts

### Non-Functional Requirements

- No performance impact (reuse loaded data)
- Mobile responsive layout
- Consistent styling with existing grid
- Accessible (screen reader friendly)

## Architecture

### Component Structure

```
[...slug].astro (lines 236-265)
  ├─ Detect: searchResult.hits.length === 0
  ├─ Set: isFallback = true
  └─ Pass props to:
       └─ listing-grid.astro
            ├─ Conditional rendering
            ├─ Empty state message (if isFallback)
            └─ Fallback results (featuredProjects)
```

### Data Flow

```
searchProperties() → {total: 0, hits: []}
  ↓
[...slug].astro detects zero
  ↓
Pass: isFallback=true, fallbackResults=featuredProjects
  ↓
listing-grid.astro renders:
  - "Không tìm thấy kết quả..." message
  - "Gợi ý cho bạn" section
  - Featured projects grid
```

## Related Code Files

### Files to Modify

1. **`src/pages/[...slug].astro`** (lines 236-265)
   - Add zero results detection
   - Prepare fallback data
   - Pass to listing-grid

2. **`src/components/listing/listing-grid.astro`**
   - Add `isFallback` prop
   - Add `fallbackResults` prop
   - Conditional rendering logic
   - Fallback UI components

### Files to Reference (No Changes)

- `src/services/elasticsearch/property-search-service.ts` - search logic
- `src/services/featured-projects/featured-projects-service.ts` - featured data
- `src/components/property/property-card.astro` - card component

## Implementation Steps

### Step 1: Detect Zero Results in `[...slug].astro`

After line 243 (parallel data loading), add:

```typescript
const [searchResult, featuredProjects, sideBlocks] = await Promise.all([...]);

// NEW: Detect zero results and prepare fallback
const hasResults = searchResult.hits.length > 0;
const isFallback = !hasResults;
const fallbackResults = isFallback ? featuredProjects.slice(0, 6) : [];
```

### Step 2: Pass Props to listing-grid.astro

Update line ~265:

```astro
<ListingGrid
  properties={searchResult.hits}
  isFallback={isFallback}
  fallbackResults={fallbackResults}
/>
```

### Step 3: Update listing-grid.astro Props

Add to Astro.props:

```typescript
interface Props {
  properties: PropertySearchHit[];
  isFallback?: boolean;
  fallbackResults?: PropertySearchHit[];
}

const { properties, isFallback = false, fallbackResults = [] } = Astro.props;
```

### Step 4: Implement Fallback Rendering

Replace existing empty state (lines 20-41) with:

```astro
{properties.length === 0 ? (
  <div class="space-y-8">
    {/* Empty State Message */}
    <div class="text-center py-12">
      <div class="mb-4">
        <svg class="mx-auto h-12 w-12 text-gray-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">
        Không tìm thấy kết quả phù hợp với tiêu chí tìm kiếm
      </h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
        Thử điều chỉnh bộ lọc hoặc xem các gợi ý bên dưới
      </p>
    </div>

    {/* Fallback Suggestions */}
    {isFallback && fallbackResults.length > 0 && (
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800">
          Gợi ý cho bạn
        </h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          {fallbackResults.map((property) => (
            <PropertyCard property={property} />
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    )}
  </div>
) : (
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
    {properties.map((property) => (
      <PropertyCard property={property} />
    ))}
  </div>
)}
```

### Step 5: Add Visual Distinction (Optional)

Add subtle badge to fallback cards:

```astro
{isFallback && (
  <span class="absolute top-2 left-2 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded">
    Gợi ý
  </span>
)}
```

## Todo List

- [ ] Modify `[...slug].astro` to detect zero results
- [ ] Pass `isFallback` and `fallbackResults` props
- [ ] Update `listing-grid.astro` props interface
- [ ] Implement fallback UI rendering
- [ ] Add empty state icon and messaging
