## Success Criteria

- ✅ Zero results shows featured projects instead of blank page
- ✅ Clear messaging: "Không tìm thấy kết quả..." + "Gợi ý cho bạn"
- ✅ Reuses existing data (no extra API calls)
- ✅ Responsive on mobile/tablet/desktop
- ✅ No console errors or warnings

## Testing Checklist

- [ ] Navigate to URL with impossible filters (e.g., 50 bedrooms)
- [ ] Verify empty state message displays
- [ ] Verify featured projects show in fallback section
- [ ] Click fallback property card → navigates correctly
- [ ] Test on mobile viewport (< 768px)
- [ ] Test with featured projects = 0 (edge case)
- [ ] Test with screen reader (accessibility)

## Risk Assessment

| Risk | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|--------|------------|
| Featured projects not relevant | Low | Phase 2 will add smart relaxation |
| Featured projects = 0 | Low | Handle gracefully, show message only |
| Mobile layout breaks | Low | Test responsive grid early |

## Security Considerations

- No user input involved (read-only)
- Reuses existing property data (already sanitized)
- No XSS risk (standard Astro templating)

## Next Steps

After Phase 1 completion:
1. Deploy to staging for user testing
2. Gather metrics (bounce rate, click-through on fallback)
3. Proceed to Phase 2: Filter relaxation service
